    <p><img style="float: right;" src="/images/steve/media_1375271038051.png" alt="media_1375271038051.png" width="228" height="138" />We often recommend using Views Slideshow as a powerful way to create slideshows in Drupal.</p>
<p>However, using Views Slideshow requires quite a lot of Drupal expertise. You need to understand Views, image styles and you often need some theming skills too. <a href="http://www.ostraining.com/courses/class/drupal/slideshow?task=view">Our Views Slideshow class</a> is over 20 videos long.</p>
<p>Nivo Slider is an alternative to Views Slideshow. It's less flexible, but is far simpler to use and looks great straight out-of-the-box.</p>
<p>Nivo Slider is a hugely popular jQuery slider that's been downloaded more than 2 million times. Originally designed for WordPress, it's available as a Drupal module.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/pikcLiAy2_E" height="1" width="1"/>
